        <abstract>
            <p>Comments on experience of being a father.</p> 
<p>Discusses possible English edition of <hi rend="italic">Generelle Morphologie</hi>. Mentions necessary revisions.</p>  
<p>Thanks CD for comment on <hi rend="italic">Natürliche Schöpfungsgeschichte</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Discusses problem of assigning specific times to origin of classes.</p>
        </abstract>
